sequenceDiagram
  participant SQL as SQL Engine
  participant ASM as ASM
  participant CELL as Storage Cell
  participant DB as DB Server
  SQL->>ASM: Full scan/direct path éligible
  ASM->>CELL: Demande blocs et prédicats
  CELL->>CELL: Predicate filtering + column projection
  CELL->>CELL: Storage Index / HCC si applicable
  CELL-->>DB: Seulement les lignes/colonnes utiles
  DB-->>SQL: Résultat final
